ERRATA.

Page ii, line 1, omit Moulmein.

— iv, line 18, at 21 hours, for 1·1 read 0·1.
— iv, line 22, at 21 hours, for 2·1 read 1·1.
— iv, line 23, at 21 hours, for 0·52 read 0·27.
— iv, line 24, in the line of Oscillation, for 1·33, 1·28, &c., and
— ii, line 15, in the line of Batavia, Spring, for 1·33, 1·28, &c. read
1·48, 1·43, 1·38, 1·55, 1·40, 0·58, 0·00, 0·15, 0·38, 0·80, 1·28, 1·78, 2·21, 2·25, 1·95, 1·60, 1·35, 1·08, 0·73, . . . . 1·25

— vi, line 11, at 21 hours, for 1·2 read 0·2.
— vi, line 15, at 21 hours, for 1·9 read 0·9.
— vi, line 16, at 21 hours, for 0·47 read 0·22.
— vi, line 17, in the line of Oscillation, for 1·50, 1·46, &c., and
— ii, line 32, in the line of Batavia, Spring, for 1·50, 1·46, &c. read
1·60, 1·56, 1·40, 1·50, 1·38, 0·48, 0·00, 0·10, 0·60, 1·23, 1·93, 2·58, 3·13, 3·28, 3·06, 2·60, 2·36, 1·98, 1·50, . . . . 1·68.

— x and xi, line 1, for the sign (?) read scale divisions.
— xl, last line but one at 21 hours, for 1·1 read 0·1.
